{"title_page": "Sakshi (novel)", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=January 2020}}\n{{Infobox book\n| name          = Sakshi\n| title_orig    = \n| translator    = \n| image         = SL-Bhyrappa-Sakshi.jpg\n| image_size    = 265px \n| caption       = ''Cover of novel's 2017-18 publication''\n| author        = [[S L Bhyrappa|S.L. Bhyrappa]]\n| illustrator   = \n| cover_artist  = \n| country       = [[India]]\n| language      = [[Kannada]]\n| series        = \n| subject       = \n| genre         = \n| published     = 1986, Sahitya Bhandara, Bangalore\n| media_type    = Print ([[Paperback]])\n| pages         = \n| isbn          = \n| oclc          = \n| preceded_by   = [[Nele (novel)|Nele]]\n| followed_by   = [[Anchu (novel)|Anchu]]\n| website       = [http://slbhyrappa.in/sakshi-the-witness/ ''Official website'']\n}}\n'''''Sakshi''''' ''(meaning: The witness)'' is a novel written by [[S L Bhyrappa|S.L. Bhyrappa]], which was first published in 1986.<ref name=\"R1\">{{cite web |url=http://slbhyrappa.in/sakshi-the-witness/ |title=Sakshi |publisher=slbhyrappa.in |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180609073838/http://slbhyrappa.in/sakshi-the-witness/ |archivedate=2018-06-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://prekshaa.in/myths-legends-rituals-bhyrappas-novels-2/ |title=Myths, Legends and Rituals in Bhyrappa\u2019s Novels \u2013 Part 2 |publisher=prekshaa.in |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508185316/http://prekshaa.in/myths-legends-rituals-bhyrappas-novels-2/ |archivedate=2018-05-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bangalorefirst.in/?p=15725 |title=Dr. S.L. Bhyrappa to be National Professor |publisher=bangalorefirst.in |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509012752/http://www.bangalorefirst.in/?p=15725 |archivedate=2018-05-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.outlookindia.com/magazine/story/a-storyteller-in-search-of-an-ending/284084 |title=A Storyteller In Search Of An Ending |publisher=Outlook |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508185414/https://www.outlookindia.com/magazine/story/a-storyteller-in-search-of-an-ending/284084 |archivedate=2018-05-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13421436-saakshi |title=\u0cb8\u0cbe\u0c95\u0ccd\u0cb7\u0cbf (Saakshi) |publisher=goodreads.com |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209073550/https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13421436-saakshi |archivedate=2018-02-09 }}</ref> As of May 2018, it had 9 reprints and has been translated into [[Hindi]] and [[English language]]s.<ref name=\"R1\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://delhipubliclibrary.in/cgi-bin/koha/opac-detail.pl?biblionumber=148306&query_desc=au:%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE,%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B8.%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B2.|title=\u0938\u093e\u0915\u094d\u0937\u0940 / \u090f\u0938. \u090f\u0932 \u092d\u0948\u0930\u092a\u094d\u092a\u093e|publisher=delhipubliclibrary.in|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180609073838/http://delhipubliclibrary.in/cgi-bin/koha/opac-detail.pl?biblionumber=148306&query_desc=au:%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE,%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B8.%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B2.|archivedate=2018-06-09}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n=== S.L. Bhyrappa's novels ===\n\n{{div col|colwidth=18em}}\n*[[Bheemakaaya]]\n*[[Dharmashree]]\n*[[Doora saridaru]]\n*[[Matadana]]\n*[[Naayi Neralu (novel)|Naayi Neralu]]\n*[[Tabbaliyu Neenade Magane (novel)|Tabbaliyu Neenade Magane]]\n*[[Gruhabhanga]]\n*[[Nirakarana]]\n*[[Grahana (novel)|Grahana]]\n*[[Daatu]]\n*[[Anveshana (novel)|Anveshana]]\n*[[Parva (novel)|Parva]]\n*[[Nele (novel)|Nele]]\n*[[Anchu (novel)|Anchu]]\n*[[Tantu]]\n*[[Saartha]]\n*[[Mandra (novel)|Mandra]]\n*[[Aavarana]]\n*[[Kavalu]]\n*[[Yaana (novel)|Yaana]]\n*[[Uttarakaanda (novel)|Uttarakaanda]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n=== S.L. Bhyrappa's autobiography ===\n\n*[[Bhitti]]\n{{clear}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Kannada novels]]\n[[Category:1986 novels]]\n[[Category:1986 Indian novels]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2020}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=January 2020}}\n{{Infobox book\n| name          = Sakshi\n| title_orig    = \n| translator    = \n| image         = SL-Bhyrappa-Sakshi.jpg\n| image_size    = 265px \n| caption       = ''Cover of novel's 2017-18 publication''\n| author        = [[S L Bhyrappa|S.L. Bhyrappa]]\n| illustrator   = \n| cover_artist  = \n| country       = [[India]]\n| language      = [[Kannada]]\n| series        = \n| subject       = \n| genre         = \n| published     = 1986, Sahitya Bhandara, Bangalore\n| media_type    = Print ([[Paperback]])\n| pages         = \n| isbn          = \n| oclc          = \n| preceded_by   = [[Nele (novel)|Nele]]\n| followed_by   = [[Anchu (novel)|Anchu]]\n| website       = [http://slbhyrappa.in/sakshi-the-witness/ ''Official website'']\n}}\n'''''Sakshi''''' ''(meaning: The witness)'' is a novel written by [[S L Bhyrappa|S.L. Bhyrappa]], which was first published in 1986.<ref name=\"R1\">{{cite web |url=http://slbhyrappa.in/sakshi-the-witness/ |title=Sakshi |publisher=slbhyrappa.in |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180609073838/http://slbhyrappa.in/sakshi-the-witness/ |archivedate=2018-06-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://prekshaa.in/myths-legends-rituals-bhyrappas-novels-2/ |title=Myths, Legends and Rituals in Bhyrappa\u2019s Novels \u2013 Part 2 |publisher=prekshaa.in |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508185316/http://prekshaa.in/myths-legends-rituals-bhyrappas-novels-2/ |archivedate=2018-05-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bangalorefirst.in/?p=15725 |title=Dr. S.L. Bhyrappa to be National Professor |publisher=bangalorefirst.in |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180509012752/http://www.bangalorefirst.in/?p=15725 |archivedate=2018-05-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.outlookindia.com/magazine/story/a-storyteller-in-search-of-an-ending/284084 |title=A Storyteller In Search Of An Ending |publisher=Outlook |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508185414/https://www.outlookindia.com/magazine/story/a-storyteller-in-search-of-an-ending/284084 |archivedate=2018-05-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13421436-saakshi |title=\u0cb8\u0cbe\u0c95\u0ccd\u0cb7\u0cbf (Saakshi) |publisher=goodreads.com |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209073550/https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13421436-saakshi |archivedate=2018-02-09 }}</ref> As of May 2018, it had 9 reprints and has been translated into [[Hindi]] and [[English language]]s.<ref name=\"R1\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://delhipubliclibrary.in/cgi-bin/koha/opac-detail.pl?biblionumber=148306&query_desc=au:%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE,%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B8.%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B2.|title=\u0938\u093e\u0915\u094d\u0937\u0940 / \u090f\u0938. \u090f\u0932 \u092d\u0948\u0930\u092a\u094d\u092a\u093e|publisher=delhipubliclibrary.in|url-status=live|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180609073838/http://delhipubliclibrary.in/cgi-bin/koha/opac-detail.pl?biblionumber=148306&query_desc=au:%E0%A4%AD%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE,%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B8.%20%E0%A4%8F%E0%A4%B2.|archivedate=2018-06-09}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n=== S.L. Bhyrappa's novels ===\n\n{{div col|colwidth=18em}}\n*[[Bheemakaaya]]\n*[[Dharmashree]]\n*[[Doora saridaru]]\n*[[Matadana]]\n*[[Naayi Neralu (Novel)|Naayi Neralu]]\n*[[Tabbaliyu Neenade Magane (novel)|Tabbaliyu Neenade Magane]]\n*[[Gruhabhanga]]\n*[[Nirakarana]]\n*[[Grahana (novel)|Grahana]]\n*[[Daatu]]\n*[[Anveshana (novel)|Anveshana]]\n*[[Parva (novel)|Parva]]\n*[[Nele (novel)|Nele]]\n*[[Anchu (novel)|Anchu]]\n*[[Tantu]]\n*[[Saartha]]\n*[[Mandra (novel)|Mandra]]\n*[[Aavarana]]\n*[[Kavalu]]\n*[[Yaana (novel)|Yaana]]\