 Literature |publisher=swarajyamag.com |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508185339/https://swarajyamag.com/culture/dr-s-l-bhyrappa-a-life-in-literature |archivedate=2018-05-08 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17345873-grahana |title=\u0c97\u0ccd\u0cb0\u0cb9\u0ca3 (Grahana) |publisher=goodreads.com |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170530151212/http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17345873-grahana |archivedate=2017-05-30 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.scribd.com/doc/224132673/Grahana-S-L-Bhyrappa |title=Grahana - S.L.Bhyrappa |publisher=scribd.com |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180609073750/https://www.scribd.com/doc/224132673/Grahana-S-L-Bhyrappa |archivedate=2018-06-09 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://vslib.kar.nic.in/newbks-aug2012.pdf |title=SECRETARIAT LIBRARY, VIDHANA SOUDHA |publisher=vslib.kar.nic.in |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508185555/http://vslib.kar.nic.in/newbks-aug2012.pdf |archivedate=2018-05-08 }}</ref> As of May 2018, it had 11 reprints.<ref name=\"R1\"/>\n\n==See also==\n=== S.L. Bhyrappa's novels ===\n\n{{div col|colwidth=18em}}\n*''[[Bheemakaaya]]''\n*''[[Dharmashree]]''\n*''[[Doora saridaru]]''\n*''[[Matadana]]''\n*''[[Naayi Neralu (novel)|Naayi Neralu]]''\n*''[[Tabbaliyu Neenade Magane (novel)|Tabbaliyu Neenade Magane]]''\n*''[[Gruhabhanga]]''\n*''[[Nirakarana]]''\n*''[[Daatu]]''\n*''[[Anveshana (novel)|Anveshana]]''\n*''[[Parva (novel)|Parva]]''\n*''[[Nele (novel)|Nele]]''\n*''[[Sakshi (novel)|Sakshi]]''\n*''[[Anchu (novel)|Anchu]]''\n*''[[Tantu]]''\n*''[[Saartha]]''\n*''[[Mandra (novel)|Mandra]]''\n*''[[Aavarana]]''\n*''[[Kavalu]]''\n*''[[Yaana (novel)|Yaana]]''\n*''[[Uttarakaanda (novel)|Uttarakaanda]]''\n{{div col end}} \n\n=== S.L. Bhyrappa's autobiography ===\n\n*[[Bhitti]]\n{{clear}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Kannada novels]]\n[[Category:1972 novels]]\n[[Category: